{"id": "e5965589f9be207303ff77ef683aa870cb2699af8f09a66eb4f52a80a2a66dd9", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:31", "text": "Highlights of Stylized Looks :"}
{"id": "0904948219fa8c7bf3070db1903c71dd1d9c554d692a9b0e787f57b274129841", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:32", "text": "Render in RenderMan .. Post Processed with Stylized Looks"}
{"id": "fab79919293df071eb060784a14eabb7fa7b6a6c02eaba242c63260cdf6bcd1d", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:33", "text": "Stylized Looks are a pixel-by-pixel post-process that is applied after your image is rendered (or during an IPR session), handled by 3 various Display Filters (PxrStylizedToon / PxrStylizedLines / PxrStylizedHatching)"}
{"id": "0cd7e53e3632f8f5014570c5bee452833f43eec8ba913c4b418f3e4c2ec8ecfa", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:34", "text": "Create your scenes using all the tools within the powerful RenderMan toolkit, including PxrSurface, Lama, and RenderMan lights .. then transform to Stylized Looks!"}
{"id": "8db693c9edfbe71e9f3a3fceaa80e3e6d9f8bfa95a3a06bc2d3368a5112df056", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:35", "text": "Mix Photorealistic & Stylized ... all in one render!"}
{"id": "06ea9905a1a888aa59724bb6bb26a551af7d79f8a54ed3b3d3ff98ae6387bb7e", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:36", "text": "Create incredible imagery using RenderMan Lights to control the transition between photoreal and stylized."}
{"id": "8378406c0b94f0e187e8ea0380aa11befaadc6a5e15e9b4bae741a675ce1579f", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:37", "text": "For instance, use the beam from a PxrRectLight to add hatching to a photoreal render.  Wherever the light strikes ... hatching is applied"}
{"id": "5ab859c5be503b9562e60ab178f80de9a026309dd4eb0cb9297fc46c7790c87f", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:38", "text": "Create your own textures sets"}
{"id": "1197a0dc2256114597a35b662528eb7cf2871509c39b8e872e404daa11c54451", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:39", "text": "Stylized Looks not only ships with a number of texture presets, but you also can create and use your own unique texture sets."}
{"id": "ad1046f4438938ba674d2d5651a845e49f93de3f7febb0f302b20c36f8153761", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:40", "text": "Need a specific NPR to look at?  No problem ... create your own hatching texture sets!"}
{"id": "0101e407e6499b2106e57452a7013d20d5fdd218bff16c8e518c56058906cfe0", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:41", "text": "Toon + Illustrative/Hatching Lighting + Lines"}
{"id": "2562fd93265d32143922a3085716562c6bc7730bf561f6d49a78274785a85b6f", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:42", "text": "Toon"}
{"id": "d269f269a4dc1b22fd3f395ee61a4a95121234762ed17505690ec1ae28484e42", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:43", "text": ": Quantize any signal per light (diffuse, spec, refraction, …) with controllable steps"}
{"id": "e7b296a9d906696bec435ee1e9936a1aac70b8cf47f11927aaae4f8c3dcad364", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:44", "text": "Illustrative Hatching Lighting:"}
{"id": "f4471b5cbad333dc180076ae35d985c3f3ca22d629a809e3bc12e8730e1e0d44", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:45", "text": "Dynamically based on light or camera depth for illustrative light & shadow rendering"}
{"id": "3b26a5427458edd20c9ec7f0954847adb8e0e692f739cc1bca3ab7438bc9c171", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:46", "text": "Lines"}
{"id": "fe52a3f36037d8be03173322c6e4bdf02e2fa61fb035ec0ce41225d9e48eb5b2", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:47", "text": ": Linework with line thickness, line thickness by lighting, line thickness by custom per object, line color by albedo, line color by lighting, line color by custom per object settings"}
{"id": "315f04f01b15b3c01c23a2d049bd185a3f7b16da132ac17510a3356e87c7a08a", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:48", "text": "Mix & Match Styles"}
{"id": "0943774e3fa85c31dcc560167d1587d1768d6937ec8eaa4e7483d2485e7a6d36", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:49", "text": "Mix and match unique and creative combinations of PxrStylizedToon / PxrStylizedLines / PxrStylizedHatching display filters"}
{"id": "01dbed95d8bb006bf84d13714a61a2f3a503eac63792046c39ac091389114a39", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:50", "text": "Try layering multiple PxrStylizedLines, each with a different thickness to create beautiful and artistic interior and exterior linework."}
{"id": "22ffc9c4cc6d19c5953aca15eecd34972e745083cdd0991e6b516a3806368d8e", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:51", "text": "Global and per-object control"}
{"id": "36f3818350b1d38e17c60ca8167204804a57b85c98eb5a15e18b8ecca10b9194", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:52", "text": "Attach the PxrStylizedControl to your PxrSurface & LamaSurface nodes to control your entire scene or per object."}
{"id": "304571923cf16284282ef325b4b58721ea9432042b1483bb4d5b730834521c83", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:53", "text": "Control different line thicknesses/coloring for certain objects"}
{"id": "17e4a581469d1db4c962dba99071a89b168a618dd5f321c086bba303d5fcec70", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:54", "text": "Export AOVs for extra refinement"}
{"id": "7649b4b2a50eb8417a10efa343cf6ac5e8adf308834526b5e7d95da624ba1913", "item_id": "2e5ba288f1:55", "text": "All AOVs associated with Stylized Looks can be exported for further creative refinement and layering outside of RenderMan"}
